3: Total Eclipse Of The Sun; Einsturzende Neubaten; Total Eclipse Of The Sun; 1999
4: Gold (12'' mix); Spandau Ballet; single; 1983
5: Zaćmienie Słońca; Józef Skrzek; Ojciec Chrzestny Dominika; 1980
6: Tangerine; The Flower Kings; Islands; 2020
7: Moondance; Nightwish; Oceanborn; 1998
8: Walking in The Air; Nightwish; Oceanborn; 1998